          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "After long minutes of touching, pushing, caressing, and eventually punching the various controls, you touch the right combination of \u201cbuttons.\u201d The whole panel suddenly ripples, steel flowing and splashing like a vertical pool, before a three dimensional map of the nearby arcology corridors rises up out of the quicksilver substance. You touch more controls, zooming in on a specific part of the map."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose:"
        },
        {
